@startuml build-system
!theme plain

package "Système de Build CMake" {
  [CMakeLists.txt principal] as MainCMake
  [cmake/CobolFunctions.cmake] as CobolFunctions
  [src/CMakeLists.txt] as SrcCMake
  [tests/CMakeLists.txt] as TestsCMake
  
  MainCMake --> CobolFunctions : inclut
  MainCMake --> SrcCMake : ajoute sous-répertoire
  MainCMake --> TestsCMake : ajoute sous-répertoire
  
  note right of CobolFunctions
    Définit les fonctions:
    - add_cobol_executable()
    - add_cobol_module()
  end note
  
  note right of SrcCMake
    - Compile les modules
    - Compile l'exécutable principal
    - Crée les liens symboliques
    - Génère run_app.sh
  end note
  
  note right of TestsCMake
    - Compile les tests
    - Génère run_tests.sh
    - Configure CTest
  end note
}

@enduml
